=== Creating Foo ===
Foo created with Bar (RC=1), Baz (RC=1)
Foo RC after alloc/init: 1

=== Relinquishing Foo (simulate transfer to thread) ===
Foo RC after retain: 2
Foo RC after relinquish: 3

=== Gaining Foo back (simulate return from thread) ===
Foo RC after gain: 3
Foo RC after autorelease: 3

=== Releasing Foo ===
Foo RC after explicit release: 2

=== Draining pool (should release Foo once more) ===
Foo finalize, releasing Baz (RC=1) implicitly
Foo dealloc, releasing Bar (RC=1) explicitly
Bar dealloc
Baz dealloc

=== Done ===
